------------
INTRODUCTION
------------

1)
SiteManager is an Open Source Web Application Framework for PHP 
Developers with an extendable system of modules and templates, 
a library of integrated functions, and SmartForms.

2)
SiteManager is an Open Source Web Application Framework for PHP 
Developers that includes a framework for code modules and layout
templates, database connectivity, SmartForms and other 
tools for web developers. All parts of the system are integrated 
through our object oriented libraries that allow for easy 
expandability and maintenance.


------------
INSTALLATION
------------

See the INSTALL file in the doc/ directory

Detailed documentation can be found in the SiteMamager manual and
API reference, both of which are a seperate download.
See http://www.phpsitemanager.com/ for more information. 
    


